---
title: Smart Mexican-Inspired Chicken Patties with Tomato, Charred Corn and Spinach Salad
description: Shake up dinner time with a loaded smart salad of savoury Mexican-spiced chicken patties, spinach, tomatoes, charred corn and, of course, tangy feta cheese to tie it all together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smart-mexican-inspired-chicken-patties-85a1b3d7.jpg
